---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Prime Citation privacy policy.">

<nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-navy-900/90 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-slate-800/50">
  <div class="container-site flex items-center h-16">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight text-white">PRIME</span>
      <span class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-gold-400">Citation</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="container-site py-16 max-w-3xl">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="text-slate-400 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>
    <p>Prime Citation is a brand under Kelly Green Holdings. We collect minimal information necessary to provide our services.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you subscribe, we collect your name, email, and billing information. If you contact us, we receive the information you provide.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information solely to deliver our services and communicate with you. We do not sell or share your personal information.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p><a href="mailto:hello@primecitation.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-dark">hello@primecitation.com</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="container-site py-10 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
  <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Prime Citation. A Kelly Green Holdings company.</p>
</footer>

</Layout>
